OL,3,CNine-hour A&E nightmare robbed our two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son of a chance to survive
OL,6,F"He was just filled with joy," his
OL,7,Fmother Liz tells me.
OL,9,FFinny was about to turn three years
OL,10,Fold, when David and Liz Roberts paid
OL,11,Fthe ultimate price of "catastrophic"
OL,12,FNHS failings.
OL,14,F"He woke up with a tummy ache,"
OL,15,Fexplains Liz.
OL,17,F"We took him to A&E and that's when
OL,18,Feverything deteriorated."
