OL,3,CNine-hour A&E nightmare robbed our two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son of a chance to survive
OL,6,FThe paediatric A&E department at
OL,7,FWhittington Hospital in North London
OL,8,Fon that summer's evening was busy and
OL,9,Funder-staffed.
OL,11,F"It was a nine-hour NHS nightmare,"
OL,12,Fsays David.
OL,14,F"After a number of hours I pushed my
OL,15,Fway through to actually get him seen
OL,16,Fproperly.
OL,18,F"We spent the majority of the time
OL,19,Fsitting in chairs in the corridor. He
OL,20,Fwas examined on my knee in the
OL,21,Fcorridor."
