OL,3,CNine-hour A&E nightmare robbed our two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son of a chance to survive
OL,6,F"The government, the politicians,
OL,7,Fneed, for once in their lives, to be
OL,8,Fdecisive."
OL,10,FLiz tells me it's difficult to have
OL,11,Fconfidence after everything they have
OL,12,Fbeen through.
OL,14,F"I hope that it will get better and I
OL,15,Fhope that no other families have to
OL,16,Fendure what we have - but I'm not
OL,17,Foptimistic."
OL,19,FIt's been almost a year since Finny
OL,20,Fdied.
