OL,6,FDavid says "language isn't sufficient"
OL,7,Fto convey their pain. He describes it
OL,8,Fsimply as an "eternal flatness".
OL,10,F"He was our much loved only-child,"
OL,11,Fsays Liz.
OL,13,F"Life without him is intolerable. We
OL,14,Fthink of him all the time. We miss him
OL,15,Fdesperately."
